### <span style="color: orange"> Requires authentication </span> ###

Creates a new reservation by specifying:
- checkin: the checkin date in the YYYY-MM-DD format;
- checkout: the checkout date in the YYYY-MM-DD format;
- pet_rooms: an array of objects, each specifying a pet (by its id) and a room type (also by its id) in which to accomodate that pet;
- services: an array of objects, each specifying a service (by its id) and the corresponding amount.

